Effective java Summary

-	Instance Controlled Class
-	Immutable class
-	Singleton class
-	Interfaced based framework
-	Service Provider framework : a system in which multiple service providers implement a service, and the system makes the implementations available to its clients, decoupling them from the implementations.
	-	Three Essential components of a service provider framework:
		1.	A service interface : which providers implement
		2.	A Provider Registration API : which system uses to register implementations, giving clients access to them,
		3.	A Service Access API : which clients use to obtain an instance of the service.